<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Transaction Rejected</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f44336;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .error-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            color: #f44336;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .transaction-details {
            background-color: white;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 5px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .refund-info {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>‚ùå Payment Not Confirmed</h1>
        <p>Your transaction has been rejected</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="error-icon">‚ö†Ô∏è</div>
        
        <p>Dear <strong>{{userName}}</strong>,</p>
        
        <p>We regret to inform you that your payment could not be confirmed and your transaction has been rejected. This may be due to insufficient funds, incorrect payment details, or other payment-related issues.</p>
        
        <div class="transaction-details">
            <h3>Transaction Details</h3>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Transaction ID:</span>
                <span>#{{transactionId}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Event:</span>
                <span>{{eventTitle}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Ticket Type:</span>
                <span>{{ticketType}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Quantity:</span>
                <span>{{quantity}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Amount:</span>
                <span>IDR {{finalAmount}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Status:</span>
                <span style="color: #f44336; font-weight: bold;">{{status}}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="detail-row">
                <span class="detail-label">Date:</span>
                <span>{{date}}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="refund-info">
            <h4>üîÑ Refund Information</h4>
            <p>Don't worry! Any points, vouchers, or coupons used in this transaction have been automatically restored to your account. The event seats have also been released back to the available pool.</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you believe this is an error or if you would like to try again, please contact the event organizer or create a new transaction.</p>
        
        <p>We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause.</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
